Dialogue: 100,0:00:03.69,0:00:09.49,Default,Pencil Knight,0,0,0,,{\q2}Want to take out the unique monster, \NWethermon the Tombguard, with just the three of us?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.79,0:00:19.04,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Huh?! A unique monster?!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:19.04,0:00:20.25,Default,Pencil Knight,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.25,0:00:23.50,Default,Pencil Knight,0,0,0,,Wethermon is likely a "special condition" type.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:23.80,0:00:26.17,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Possibilities that come to mind...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:26.17,0:00:29.05,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"Pick up or destroy a particular in-game object."
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.05,0:00:30.47,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"Last a certain length of time."
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.47,0:00:32.51,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"Survive a particular attack."
Dialogue: 100,0:00:33.18,0:00:37.18,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}You occasionally see \N"persuade in the middle of battle," too.{You occasionally see "reason with him in the middle of battle," too.}
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.18,0:00:39.14,Default,Katzo Tataki,0,0,0,,Any idea on what the condition is?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.64,0:00:41.81,Default,Pencil Knight,0,0,0,,I've tried a few different things...{I've tried a few different things,}
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.48,Default,Pencil Knight,0,0,0,,and I think it's "Last a certain length of time."
Dialogue: 100,0:00:45.19,0:00:50.57,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\i1}Wethermon the Tombguard's \Ncombat conditions change as time passes.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.11,0:00:55.20,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}First, we need to survive the ten minutes of the first phase.{First, we need to survive the ten minutes of Phase 1.}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.92,0:01:05.25,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't let your memories be sad ones.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:09.38,0:01:11.22,Default,Setsuna,0,0,0,,Please put Wethermon...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.59,0:01:14.47,Default,Setsuna,0,0,0,,Please put my love to rest.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.37,0:03:04.41,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.62,0:03:06.42,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,A Rebirth Tearjewel?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:06.92,0:03:08.67,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,It's a resurrection item.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.67,0:03:14.22,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,If you use it on a disabled player within ten seconds,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.22,0:03:18.14,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,you can revive them with full HP.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.39,0:03:19.72,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Oh, you can do that?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.10,0:03:21.68,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,It's a god-tier item, then!{That's a god-tier item, then!}
Dialogue: 100,0:03:23.89,0:03:28.56,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}I went from town to town this morning \Nand bought all twelve that were for sale.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.06,0:03:31.86,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Use them carefully, now.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.61,0:03:35.36,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,They cost four million mahni apiece.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.36,0:03:38.11,Default,Sunraku/Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Four million?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.53,0:03:41.45,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,We'll get four Rebirth Tearjewels each.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.45,0:03:44.12,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Then there's this, which lets you revive at half your max HP.{Then there's this, which lets you revive at half your max HP—}
Dialogue: 100,0:03:44.95,0:03:47.54,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,The Divine Lifesalve, and we each get five.{the Divine Lifesalve— of which we each get five.}
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.88,0:03:51.42,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}That's the max number of extra lives \Nyou can get in this game.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:52.17,0:03:56.13,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}We'll use these 27 resurrection items \Nto challenge Wethermon the Tombguard.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.09,0:03:57.88,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.72,0:04:01.64,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}Sunraku will take point \Non holding off Wethermon's attacks.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.22,0:04:06.89,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}If you get killed, Katzo or I will revive you \Nand take over for a bit.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.14,0:04:11.27,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,And the same goes if one of us bites it, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.65,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:12.65,0:04:17.65,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}To achieve our goal of surviving long enough \Nagainst the Colossus, Wethermon,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.65,0:04:18.78,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,this is the only way.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.70,0:04:23.87,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I call it...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.29,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Zombie Tactics!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.62,0:04:29.29,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind Slash!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.55,0:04:43.30,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Katzo!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.22,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Way ahead of you!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.56,0:04:48.56,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Take this!{Take that!}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.09,0:05:18.05,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I'm tagging in until you're ready!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.34,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Any tips you got, Sunraku?!{What'd you learn, Sunraku?!}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.18,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,You can't beat him, so focus on dodging!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.43,0:05:25.18,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Well, simple enough!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.56,0:05:27.81,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,You lasted two minutes, five seconds.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.81,0:05:30.27,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,That's a record for a first encounter.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.27,0:05:31.60,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Very impressive.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.86,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,So, what do you think after mixing it up with him?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.86,0:05:38.73,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Without one impressive plan, I can tell...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.24,0:05:42.24,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,there's definitely no way I could keep up with him.{there's definitely no way I could keep pace with him.}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.91,0:05:49.00,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}Wethermon the Tombguard definitely belongs \Nin the "Seven Colossi" league with Lycagon.{Wethermon the Tombguard... He definitely belongs in the "Seven Colossi" league with Lycagon.}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.00,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind Slash!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.50,0:05:56.34,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}Well, I spent a whole lot of money \Non this "impressive plan."{Well, I spent a whole lot of money on this "impressive plan"...}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:56.34,0:05:57.63,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,So, better make it worthwhile.{So you'd better make it worthwhile.}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.13,0:06:02.30,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Four million mahni for a single respawn, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.34,0:06:08.76,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}Their durability is down to half \Nfrom just two minutes of fighting?!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.18,0:06:12.02,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}I guess you really do need a weapon \Nwith enhanced durability.{I guess you really do need a weapon with enhanced durability...}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.02,0:06:17.06,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}I got just the thing with its durability \Nraised to the max,{Time for the weapon whose durability I raised to the extreme...} Marsh Daggers V3!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.61,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Resurrection items, weapons...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.61,0:06:22.15,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}On all fronts, the battle against Wethermon \Nis one of endurance!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.53,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'm tagging in, Katzo!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.79,0:06:36.17,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll take over again if you die!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.17,0:06:36.79,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.30,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Yeah, figured that wouldn't work.{Yeah, figured that wouldn't work...}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.72,0:06:44.80,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Thunderclap!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.39,0:06:50.39,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Not that easy!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.23,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Skate Foot!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.40,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Too close!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.73,0:07:04.90,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}Thunderclap calls down \Na five-second barrage of insta-kill lightning!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.66,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Five damn seconds?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.87,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm getting the hang of this!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.87,0:07:13.66,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}Even at close range, if I run at max speed after using \NSkate Foot, I can just keep ahead of it!{Even at close range, if I use Skate Foot followed by running at max speed, I can just keep ahead of it!}
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.00,0:07:17.17,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Nimbus Fist.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.80,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Okay, got no clue on that one.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.32,0:07:45.53,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Tagging in!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.95,0:07:51.41,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind Slash!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.50,0:07:58.67,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Tagging in!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.88,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Thunderclap!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.65,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Screw all this!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.28,0:08:27.70,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I can't dodge that crap!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.66,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,{\q2}It'd be a miracle to stay alive \Nfor even thirty seconds against it!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.07,0:08:34.41,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,You've been pretty amazing, though.{You've done pretty amazingly, even so.}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.41,0:08:37.16,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,We still have about half our resurrection items left.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.37,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,You've done very well.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.79,0:08:41.79,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Y'know, you've been playing with those scales for a while.{Y'know, you've been playing with those scales for a while...}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.21,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,What's it all about?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.30,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Just preparing something.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.17,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,It might be about time to use them, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.85,0:08:58.31,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,He stopped?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.44,0:09:00.56,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Ten minutes.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.07,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Finally there, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:05.57,0:09:07.11,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Ten minutes have passed.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.82,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,It's time for the second phase.{Phase 2 begins.}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.45,0:09:18.33,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,E...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.75,0:09:22.71,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Export. Summon Call.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.84,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Tactical Mount,{Tactical Mount...}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.84,0:09:26.13,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Kirin!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.05,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Katzo!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.72,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Right, I got this!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.85,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Guess my job as resurrection backup is over.{Guess my job as resurrection backup is over...}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.85,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Just like the intel said,{Just like the intel said...}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.11,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,when you fight Wethermon for ten minutes,{When you fight Wethermon for ten minutes,}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.11,0:09:47.94,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,he summons Kirin, the robot horse!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.95,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Okay, so it's a horse,{Okay, so it's a horse...}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.95,0:09:57.58,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,but it's not exactly what I was picturing.{But it's not exactly what I was picturing.}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.29,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,This is more like...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.08,0:10:02.96,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,a dump truck with legs!{A dump truck with legs!}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.10,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Phase 2.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.10,0:10:30.61,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}Wethermon summons Kirin, \Nand you must prevent them from merging{Wethermon summons Kirin, and you must prevent them from combining}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.61,0:10:33.32,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,while surviving ten minutes, just like in the first phase.{while surviving ten minutes, just like in Phase 1.}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.74,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Katzo! You handle Kirin!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:36.41,0:10:39.79,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}If you let him stay in charge, \Nhe'll fire missiles and lasers everywhere!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.50,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,And if he combines with Wethermon,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.08,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,the whole plan'll be done for!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.67,0:10:49.00,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\t(3352,4353,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}There'll be no way to stop them from trampling us, \Nand it'll be instant death when they do.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.25,0:10:53.97,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}The only way to fight that is to stay on his back \Nand trigger his "buck-off animation."
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.97,0:10:56.22,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Easier said than done, dammit!{Easier said than done, damn it!}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.86,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,{\q2}How the hell do you expect me \Nto play cowboy with this thing?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.86,0:11:12.99,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}Didn't you play a lot of Cavalry Crisis, \Nthat mounted fighting game?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:12.99,0:11:15.11,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Show me your rodeo skills!{Show me your riding technique!}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:15.11,0:11:17.36,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Cavalry Crisis? What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.62,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I've never heard of a trash game by that name!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:19.95,0:11:22.45,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Just focus on your job!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.00,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:24.00,0:11:26.42,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Cav isn't a trash game!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:26.42,0:11:28.21,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,It's more like god-tier!{It's more like a god-tier game!}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:28.21,0:11:31.67,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,And that was still just a fighting game...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.01,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay... how do I do this?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:39.26,0:11:42.01,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,{\i1}SLF's meticulous with its world-building,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.98,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,{\i1}and thinking about that usually leads you to a solution.{and thinking about that usually leads you to a solution...}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:44.98,0:11:47.52,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words, if Kirin is a machine,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:47.52,0:11:49.40,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,{\i1}he'll need maintenance!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:50.15,0:11:52.15,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,There it is! A maintenance ladder!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.65,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Expectations met!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:54.86,0:11:55.61,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:56.99,0:11:59.57,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Every horse needs a bridle, right?!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.83,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Skill, "Whip Puppet: Snake"!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:04.12,0:12:10.00,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,{\q2}Never thought my sub-job, \N"Archaeologist," would pay off like this!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:11.13,0:12:15.09,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,{\q2}The rodeo technique of the country's \Nthird-ranked Cavalry Crisis player...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:15.09,0:12:18.38,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Have a taste, you bucking bronco!{I'll show it to you, you bucking bronco!}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:19.89,0:12:21.39,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:24.43,0:12:28.39,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Sunraku and Katzo are holding off their targets,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:28.73,0:12:31.77,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}but at this rate, we'll run out of \Nresurrection items before the time limit.{but at this rate, we'll run out of resurrection items before we hit the time limit.}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:33.57,0:12:34.94,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Now's the time to use it.{Now's the time to use it...}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.36,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,The Reward Scales!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:39.99,0:12:43.99,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}The Golden Scales is an NPC-run trading company.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:44.33,0:12:50.42,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\an8\i1}In its possession is a particular "unique item", \Na category comprising the rarest items in the game.{In its possession is a particular "unique item"—a category comprising the rarest items in the game.}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.63,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}It is known as the Reward Scales.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:54.21,0:12:57.92,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}By sacrificing items to the "offering dish" on the left side,{By sacrificing items to the left-side "offering dish,"}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:57.92,0:13:04.72,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\an8\i1}you can receive various perks \Nfrom the "blessing dish" on the right. {you can receive various perks from the right-side "blessing dish."}
Dialogue: 100,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.81,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Give me the best you've got, Scales.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:09.81,0:13:15.36,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}I did everything I could and finally persuaded \Nthe Golden Scales to lend you to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:15.77,0:13:18.82,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}The Rebirth Tearjewels aren't the only thing \NI dipped into my savings for.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:19.28,0:13:24.07,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}High-value items I've won through my exploits, \Ntraded for and bought...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:24.07,0:13:26.41,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Thirty million mahni's worth in total.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:26.41,0:13:29.33,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,And I'm offering it up!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:38.84,0:13:42.63,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Nope, nope, nope, nope, nope, nope, nope, nope, nope!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:43.59,0:13:47.43,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,The centrifugal force is gonna throw me off!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.85,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Dammit! I don't have the stamina for this!{Damn it! I don't have enough stamina for this!}
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.85,0:13:53.94,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}Even if I see the attacks coming, \Nif my stamina management is just a little off,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:53.94,0:13:55.94,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I fail to dodge it, and I die on the spot!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:56.61,0:13:58.69,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,"The scales maintain equilibrium."
Dialogue: 100,0:13:59.15,0:14:02.45,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}"Let its value be measured. \NBestow upon me the power to fight hundreds."{"Let its value be measured numerically." "Bestow upon me the power to fight hundreds."}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:03.28,0:14:07.95,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}Albeit temporarily, I can award \Nadditional stat points to others.{Albeit temporarily, I can award additional stat points to others...}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.29,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,The rate is one point per 100,000 mahni.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:11.29,0:14:15.21,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I'll use my entire savings!{My entire savings—} Three hundred points in total!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.67,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,We'll start off with fifty points each!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.93,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Take them, you thieves!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:31.85,0:14:32.68,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.90,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}My stamina's replenished?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:34.90,0:14:37.69,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... my stats got buffed!{No... my stats have increased!}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.61,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pencilgon's behind this, eh?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.95,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was wondering why she was fiddling with those windows.{I was wondering why she was fiddling with those windows...}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:47.99,0:14:50.08,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}She gave me boosts to stamina and luck!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:51.08,0:14:54.21,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It's clear I can't deal damage, no matter where I hit you.{It's clear I can't deal damage, no matter where I hit you...}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.29,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:58.79,0:15:00.88,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Infight!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:02.21,0:15:07.43,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}...it's not my first time fighting someone like that.{It's not my first time fighting someone like that.}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:09.97,0:15:15.23,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\i1}There's a combat skill \Nthat doesn't pull from strength, but from luck!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:15.64,0:15:16.73,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its name...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.86,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind...{Wind—}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:18.86,0:15:22.86,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Hand of Fortune!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.24,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,...Slash!{—Slash!}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:34.00,0:15:37.75,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,A swordsman without a sword is like curry without roux!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:38.21,0:15:40.25,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Suck on that! You're just a plate of white rice now!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:40.79,0:15:43.38,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Get yourself some pickled plums and try again later!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:43.38,0:15:44.34,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Skill...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.22,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Skate Foot!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.47,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.47,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I got your sword!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.73,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,How you like that, sucker?!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:55.73,0:15:59.73,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,And it's... so big and heavy!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:00.27,0:16:03.28,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Can't stick that in the inventory, I guess.{Can't stick that in inventory, I guess...}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:03.28,0:16:03.73,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}But...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:04.86,0:16:09.24,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\i1}Making sure he can't use that split-second \Nslash attack or the lightning strikes is huge!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:09.24,0:16:12.08,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's still got that Nimbus Fist going on,{He's still got that Nimbus Fist going on, but...}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:12.70,0:16:15.54,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I'm safe from that as long as I'm behind him.{I'm safe from that as long as I'm behind him.}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:15.54,0:16:17.96,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Knowing that will let me avoid it, no problem.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.79,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Nice work!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:21.71,0:16:24.67,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I appreciate you raising my stats and all,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:24.67,0:16:27.55,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,but that's not gonna let me stop this thing!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:27.55,0:16:30.47,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Katzo! There's about four minutes left in the second phase!{Katzo! There's about four minutes left in Phase 2!}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:30.80,0:16:33.39,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,You've got to strap in for that long!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.56,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,He'll keep to that pattern if you stay on him!{He'll keep to that pattern as long as you stay on him!}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.81,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I get it, but...{I get it, but—}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.06,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Strap{\i0} in?{Strap in...?}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:46.32,0:16:48.40,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I just got a great idea.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.03,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,A great idea?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.16,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Tidal Rush.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.08,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Close call!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:00.67,0:17:03.00,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I dodged in the nick of time,{I dodged in the nick of time...}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.09,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he almost had me there!{But he almost had me there!}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:05.05,0:17:08.09,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's gotta be an insta-kill, for sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:08.34,0:17:12.14,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\i1}They even gave him a special move set \Nif you steal his sword.{They even gave him a special move set for if you steal his sword...}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.72,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a bad field layout!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.68,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Pencilgon!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:18.14,0:17:20.64,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so focused on dodging, I ran the wrong way!{I was so focused on evading, I ran in the wrong direction!}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:22.69,0:17:24.23,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I turned his aggro on Pencilgon!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:25.65,0:17:26.40,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Tidal—
Dialogue: 100,0:17:27.28,0:17:29.15,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Eyes on the prize, Wethermon!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:30.07,0:17:31.91,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I've still got your sword!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.49,0:17:39.08,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,He can grab me from that angle, too?!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.04,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Tidal Rush.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:43.71,0:17:45.09,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Sunraku!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:49.30,0:17:51.05,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Nimbus Fist.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:54.47,0:17:58.06,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}The safe zone for Nimbus Fist is behind Wethermon!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.11,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seven, eight...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:15.66,0:18:18.99,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Let's do this from the top, Wethermon.{Let's get back to basics, Wethermon.}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.71,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind Slash!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:25.79,0:18:26.84,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Sunraku!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:26.84,0:18:30.46,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,We can't afford any more deaths!{One more death could doom our chances!}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:30.76,0:18:33.22,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}If that last attack had been anything \Nother than Nimbus Fist,
Dialogue: 100,0:18:33.22,0:18:34.47,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,he could've taken us all out!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:34.47,0:18:35.76,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Sorry, okay?!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:35.76,0:18:40.22,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}I guess he's better off with the sword! \NAt least, I know those animations!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.64,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:43.85,0:18:44.85,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Katzo?!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:45.10,0:18:47.36,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,W-W-Watch this!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:49.07,0:18:52.44,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,H-H-He can't b-b-buck me off like this!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:52.44,0:18:55.32,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I-I-I can stay on him the whole time!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:53.86,0:18:57.28,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\an8}That... was your great idea?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:57.28,0:18:58.62,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,You want me to go tighter?!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:59.41,0:19:03.25,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Fine, whatever. If that's what you're into.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:03.25,0:19:04.46,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:04.46,0:19:08.63,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,It's just gonna distract you, so it's better if you don't look.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:08.63,0:19:09.38,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:09.38,0:19:14.51,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Th-The shaking is d-d-raining my HP, I th-th-think!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:14.51,0:19:17.89,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'm b-b-built to tank damage, \Nb-b-but I might not last too long like this!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:19.81,0:19:21.10,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:27.73,0:19:28.61,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:54.59,0:19:57.68,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'm not getting a "you beat me" vibe, here.{I'm not getting a "you beat me" vibe, here...}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:58.14,0:19:59.09,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.07,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Stay on your guard, both of you.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:13.57,0:20:16.95,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Even when Ashura Kai was a halfway decent clan,
Dialogue: 100,0:20:16.95,0:20:20.12,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,we only made it this far one time.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:20.66,0:20:21.99,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:21.99,0:20:24.12,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,The second phase is over.{Phase 2 is over.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:25.66,0:20:27.58,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,The real challenge starts now.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:30.21,0:20:31.71,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Phase 3.{Phase 3...}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:38.18,0:20:41.34,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}The last time I made it here, \Nhe wiped out the Ashura Kai with his first move.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:41.97,0:20:45.60,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}When the cracks formed \Nin Wethermon the Tombguard's armor...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:48.19,0:20:52.31,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}he let out a howl and unleashed a shock wave \Nacross the entire field.{He let out a howl and unleashed a shock wave across the entire field.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:54.27,0:20:58.90,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}When it hit us, all our buffs and armor \Ndidn't matter a bit. We died instantly.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:58.90,0:21:01.99,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Sounds like a pretty solid death sentence.{Sounds like a pretty solid death sentence...}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:02.45,0:21:04.74,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,But you look like you've got a plan.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:07.83,0:21:09.79,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:09.79,0:21:13.25,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,If this doesn't do the trick, try to dodge him as best you can.{If this doesn't do the trick, try to dodge it as best you can.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:14.50,0:21:19.22,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,In SLF, the keys to victory come from the story.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:19.76,0:21:25.85,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'd always assumed he was some kind of cyborg, \Nwho'd modified his body with technology from the Divinity.{I'd always assumed Wethermon was some kind of cyborg, who'd modified his body with technology from the Divinity...}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:26.85,0:21:27.52,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:27.85,0:21:34.23,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}He called Wethermon the Tombguard \N"a living corpse" who'd "outlived his time"?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:34.44,0:21:36.90,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,That's what gave me the key.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.53,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,His classification is "undead monster"!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.16,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Holy water is effective against them!{For undead, you use holy water!}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:44.83,0:21:47.54,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,And that's not just any holy water.{And that's not just any holy water...}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:47.54,0:21:50.79,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Eristella, the Saint of Love, put her heart into it.{It's holy water the Saint of Love, Eristella, put her heart into...}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:50.79,0:21:52.79,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,So it's blessed by the saint herself!{The saint's own holy water!}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:53.25,0:21:56.34,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,It's the best potion you can get for fighting the undead!{It's the best potion for fighting the undead you can get!}
